Accueil

institute

   The aim of the Institute of Research and Technology (IRT) b<>com is to
   accelerate the development and marketing of tools, products, and
   services for improving everyday living, through research and innovation
   in digital technologies. In concrete terms, b<>com innovates at the
   highest levels in the fields of hypermedia (ultra-high-definition
   images, 3D, smart content, and virtual and augmented reality, to name a
   few), ultra-high-speed fixed and mobile networks, and its starting
   field of e-health.
     __________________________________________________________________

     * innovation
     * future
     * better life
     * great ideas
     * better experiences

   comes
   with
   bcom

About b<>com

   Created in late 2012, the b<>com Technology Research Institute is a
   tech provider and an innovation accelerator for every business that
   uses digital to increase its competitiveness. Discover b<>com in 90
   seconds thanks to this key facts and figures video.
   About b<>com

Activities

   Intellectual property, technological solutions , R&D à la carte,
   consulting, technological platforms
   Activities

Working with b<>com

   b<>com is a tool for accelerating the innovation of its investor
   members. Whether you're a large corporate group, an academic player, or
   a small or medium business, with b<>com you're choosing a partnership
   that lasts.
   Working with b<>com

b<>com Galaxy

   Board, European projects, funders, international scientific advisory
   board, members, partners, staff and training advisory board, find out
   our ecosystem, enter the b<>com galaxy!
