About b<>com

   Created in late 2012, the b<>com Technology Research Institute is a
   tech provider and an innovation accelerator for every business that
   uses digital to increase its competitiveness. Discover b<>com in 90
   seconds thanks to this key facts and figures video.
   About b<>com

